+controls: media does not settle; future-observed official does not leak (in-window=1, after-window=0)
+boundary: exactly-on-end counts (1); one-day-after does not leak; malformed/None observed_at safe
+type-safety: string-topics no spurious match; bool horizon/n not settleable; non-dict settlement rejected (no crash)
+
+ACCEPTANCE = PASS
